                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Terrell</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-09-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 21,
                                    1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Four of Miss Melton’s assailants were sentenced on the 17th instant to
                            three years’ imprisonment.</p>
